name: Mary Luella (Culver) Hall
keyDates:
1905-1980 (Age 74)

Born Nov. 16, 1905, Friday Harbor

Died April 28, 1980, Edmonds WA, age 74.

Married: George Mason Hall, July 16, 1929

Graduate of Bellingham Normal School (now WWU).

Elementary school teacher (kindergarten through 2nd grade).

Mother of George, Jerald, and Sandra (Durand).
